title: THE ASPHALT JUNGLE -- The Lady and the Lawyer ( with Vera Miles
description:
This 1961 police series based on the 1950 feature film is rare, and this is from a 16mm film print, so the video quality isn't the greatest but it's very watchable.

Later that year this episode was expanded into a 76 minute feature film called "The Lawbreakers", in which David White also appeared.

Guest Stars -- Vera Miles, Robert Douglas, Robert H. Harris, 
Ken Lynch, and John Zaremba
